org.instantplaces.purewidgets.shared.widgetmanager
Class WidgetInput

java.lang.Object
  org.instantplaces.purewidgets.shared.widgetmanager.WidgetInput

public class WidgetInput
extends java.lang.Object

The WidgetInput class represents an input from a user to an option of a widget. An input is issued by a persona and consists of a list of zero or more parameters.

Author:
Jorge C. S. Cardoso
